If vertual machine's IP is changed, what needs to be done?
(1) application.yml : database server address  (2) On VM: vim /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf


Tools used:
(1) http://www.ibootstrap.cn ==> a quick way to generate front end html codes
(2) Database viewer : Sequel Pro
(3) Interacting with REST APIs: Postman




